{"tid":1588732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢俾黑警拉 提供自己資料既方法","createTime":"2019-09-23T03:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T03:38:20.000Z","uid":231410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4b65377f59673b5ca9d162e6d86c32497ff9d0","tid":1588732,"uid":231410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"每次見到有手足俾人拉都好心痛, 依家黑警仲要想盡辦法阻止你提供個人資料俾人跟進<br />\n咁除左每次都睇相睇片認人, 仲可以點?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有!</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個出黎發夢既, 唔該出發前用Telegram send一個Schedule message!</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">方法係長按send制, 再揀你預計會安全離開現場既時間<br />\n內容當然係自己個人資料, 通知你身邊信得過既人, 話佢知你依家收到呢個message, 我好有可能已經被捕, 叫佢打電話聯絡你本人, 如果聯絡唔到, 就盡快聯絡律師/星火協助 (提供埋聯絡方式呀!)<br />\n</span><br />\nsend完你個chat會多左個icon, 顯示你有schedule send既message, 每次平安訓醒就click入去delete左個message, 下次要發夢前再準備過。<br />\n你唔鍾意用Telegram, 用email又好, 乜L都好, 只要有schedule send / delay send功能既野就可以<br />\n記住要試一次係唔係work先呀!<br />\n(唔知有無人提過......)<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求， 缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"7393dcd86029d4386e37a51ddc8b336d6d5c5b05","tid":1588732,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"2f81bfa419c314070ebca369def66eb1b2b23ee0","tid":1588732,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"[（防禦）方向討論&amp;檢討]對家玩抹黑去掩蓋警暴，我地對應手法就係訂立界線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588728</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0784672ea23d2aa0f89095cbfc0daaa1aba944a","tid":1588732,"uid":231410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:07:04.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"2d6cc03733168f649d416317c851d43cfd34fc60","tid":1588732,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0